name: Double Cube
description:
Can you navigate two cubes through a space shuttle? Tap to jump and avoid obstacles. The environment and speed of the players change rapidly. So you need to think, adjust and react in matter of split seconds.

Double Cube will test your eye-finger coordination. if you are good at multitasking, Double Cube is the right game for you. This 100% original game will get you hooked for hours. Download now and play.

Features:

- Different types of characters!
- Simple but challenging
- Unlimited gameplay
- Playable by all age people
